@@ -0,0 +1,69 @@
+# Copyright (c) 2023-2025, [Ribose Inc](https://www.ribose.com).
+# All rights reserved.
+# This file is a part of tamatebako
+#
+# Redistribution and use in source and binary forms, with or without
